        "color_scheme": "scheme-1",
        "padding_top": 0,
        "padding_bottom": 0,
        "custom_liquid": "<div class=\"page-width\" style=\"padding:30px 0 50px;\">\n\n  <!-- HERO -->\n  <div style=\"background:#152420;border-radius:14px;padding:44px 32px;text-align:center;margin-bottom:36px;\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#f4a51c;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:10px;\">About Furniva</div>\n    <h1 style=\"font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;font-size:32px;font-weight:700;color:#FFFFFF;margin:0 0 14px;\">Online Furniture Shopping in India</h1>\n    <p style=\"font-size:15px;color:#D8D3C8;max-width:600px;margin:0 auto;line-height:1.7;\">At Furniva, you'll find an array of styles, from understated and functional to bold, geometric designs tailored for modern and luxurious homes.</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- OUR STORY -->\n  <div style=\"max-width:720px;margin:0 auto 40px;\">\n    <h2 style=\"font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;font-size:24px;font-weight:700;color:#152420;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:center;\">Our Story</h2>\n    <p style=\"font-size:14.5px;color:#444;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:14px;\">Welcome to Furniva, your trusted source for high-quality, beautifully designed, and affordable furniture in India. Established in 2024, Furniva is driven by a mission to <strong>redefine how Indian homes and offices experience comfort and style.</strong></p>\n    <p style=\"font-size:14.5px;color:#444;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:14px;\">We believe that great design should be accessible to all, which is why our collection offers a wide variety of <strong>premium and minimalistic furniture</strong> pieces to elevate any space without stretching your budget.</p>\n    <p style=\"font-size:14.5px;color:#444;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:14px;\">Our product range includes everything from sleek office essentials to aesthetic home furniture that seamlessly balances form and function. At Furniva, you'll find an <strong>array of styles</strong>, from understated and functional to bold, <strong>geometric designs</strong> tailored for modern and luxurious homes.</p>\n    <p style=\"font-size:14.5px;color:#444;line-height:1.8;\">Each piece is crafted to enhance your living experience, merging quality materials with innovative design. With Furniva, it's not just furniture &mdash; it's a lifestyle upgrade.</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- WHY CHOOSE FURNIVA -->\n  <h2 style=\"font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;font-size:24px;font-weight:700;color:#152420;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:center;\">Why Choose Furniva?</h2>\n  <div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));gap:20px;margin-bottom:40px;\">\n    <div style=\"text-align:center;padding:20px;\">\n      <div style=\"width:52px;height:52px;border-radius:50%;background:#F5F0E8;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin:0 auto 14px;\">\n        <svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#152420\" stroke-width=\"1.6\"><path d=\"M9 12l2 2 4-4\"/><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"/></svg>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:#152420;margin-bottom:6px;\">Uncompromising Quality</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#666;line-height:1.6;\">We believe in delivering products that are not just beautiful but also built to last.</div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"text-align:center;padding:20px;\">\n      <div style=\"width:52px;height:52px;border-radius:50%;background:#F5F0E8;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin:0 auto 14px;\">\n        <svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#152420\" stroke-width=\"1.6\"><rect x=\"2\" y=\"6\" width=\"20\" height=\"12\" rx=\"2\"/><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"3\"/></svg>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:#152420;margin-bottom:6px;\">Affordability Redefined</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#666;line-height:1.6;\">Luxury shouldn't be a luxury. Our competitive pricing ensures you can elevate your space without breaking the bank.</div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"text-align:center;padding:20px;\">\n      <div style=\"width:52px;height:52px;border-radius:50%;background:#F5F0E8;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin:0 auto 14px;\">\n        <svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#152420\" stroke-width=\"1.6\"><path d=\"M20 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H8a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2\"/><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"7\" r=\"4\"/></svg>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:#152420;margin-bottom:6px;\">Customer Satisfaction</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#666;line-height:1.6;\">Your satisfaction is our priority. We strive to provide exceptional customer service and a hassle-free experience.</div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"text-align:center;padding:20px;\">\n      <div style=\"width:52px;height:52px;border-radius:50%;background:#F5F0E8;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin:0 auto 14px;\">\n        <svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#152420\" stroke-width=\"1.6\"><path d=\"M3 3h18v18H3z\"/><path d=\"M3 9h18M9 21V9\"/></svg>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:#152420;margin-bottom:6px;\">Diverse Range</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#666;line-height:1.6;\">From minimalist designs to bold geometric pieces, we offer a wide variety of furniture to suit every style.</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- SNAPSHOT -->\n  <div style=\"background:#F7F5F1;border-radius:12px;padding:24px 20px;display:flex;justify-content:space-around;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:16px;margin-bottom:40px;text-align:center;\">\n    <div>\n      <div style=\"font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;font-size:24px;font-weight:700;color:#152420;\">2024</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#8A6E4A;\">Est.</div>\n    </div>\n    <div>\n      <div style=\"font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;font-size:24px;font-weight:700;color:#152420;\">{{ collections.all.products_count | default: 40 }}+</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#8A6E4A;\">Products</div>\n    </div>\n    <div>\n      <div style=\"font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;font-size:24px;font-weight:700;color:#152420;\">Pan-India</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#8A6E4A;\">Delivery</div>\n    </div>\n    <div>\n      <div style=\"font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;font-size:24px;font-weight:700;color:#152420;\">Free</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#8A6E4A;\">Installation</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- SOCIALS -->\n  <div style=\"text-align:center;\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#666;margin-bottom:14px;\">Find us on social networks</div>\n    <div style=\"display:flex;justify-content:center;gap:14px;\">\n      <a href=\"https://x.com/Furniva_in\" style=\"color:#152420;\"><svg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"M18.9 1.153h3.68l-8.04 9.19L24 22.846h-7.406l-5.8-7.584-6.638 7.584H.474l8.6-9.83L0 1.154h7.594l5.243 6.932ZM17.61 20.65h2.039L6.486 3.24H4.298Z\"/></svg></a>\n      <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/furniva.in/\" style=\"color:#152420;\"><svg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"M12 2.163c3.204 0 3.584.012 4.85.07 3.252.148 4.771 1.691 4.919 4.919.058 1.265.069 1.645.069 4.849 0 3.205-.012 3.584-.069 4.849-.149 3.225-1.664 4.771-4.919 4.919-1.266.058-1.644.07-4.85.07-3.204 0-3.584-.012-4.849-.07-3.26-.149-4.771-1.699-4.919-4.92-.058-1.265-.07-1.644-.07-4.849 0-3.204.013-3.583.07-4.849.149-3.227 1.664-4.771 4.919-4.919 1.266-.057 1.645-.069 4.849-.069zm0-2.163c-3.259 0-3.667.014-4.947.072-4.358.2-6.78 2.618-6.98 6.98-.059 1.281-.073 1.689-.073 4.948 0 3.259.014 3.668.072 4.948.2 4.358 2.618 6.78 6.98 6.98 1.281.058 1.689.072 4.948.072 3.259 0 3.668-.014 4.948-.072 4.354-.2 6.782-2.618 6.979-6.98.059-1.28.073-1.689.073-4.948 0-3.259-.014-3.667-